name: Bimbo The Clueless
description:
The Academy's social butterfly. He manages to befriend everyone and I mean everyone. Gets a C+ every time.

Included in: [color=#7A6352]Hall Of Bimbo[/color]
description_schinese:
学院里的社交达人。他能和所有人交上朋友——我是真的说所有人。每次都拿 C+。

收录于：[color=#7A6352]宾博殿堂[/color]
description_tchinese:
學院的社交明星，他跟誰都能混熟——真的，誰都行。成績永遠卡在 C+，完全是個奇蹟。

收錄於：[color=#7A6352]賓博殿堂[/color]

name: Tian The Archer
description:
A horrible shot, but a good talker!

Included in: [color=#7A6352]Hall Of Bimbo[/color]
description_schinese:
射术糟糕，但嘴皮子是一流的！

收录于：[color=#7A6352]宾博殿堂[/color]
description_tchinese:
射得有夠糟，但超會講話，三兩句就把人收服。

收錄於：[color=#7A6352]賓博殿堂[/color]

name: ShoSho The Mage
description:
Average at magic, kind to a fault. Pulls a lot of all nighters.

Included in: [color=#7A6352]Hall Of Bimbo[/color]
description_schinese:
魔法水平一般，善良得过头。常常熬夜到天亮。

收录于：[color=#7A6352]宾博殿堂[/color]
description_tchinese:
魔法普通，心腸超好，常常熬夜爆肝到天亮。

收錄於：[color=#7A6352]賓博殿堂[/color]

name: Zane The Tank
description:
Big, heavy, reliable. Cannot for the life of him wield a blade. Writes letters to his siblings back home.

Included in: [color=#7A6352]Hall Of Bimbo[/color]
description_schinese:
又大又重、可靠稳健。就是打死都握不好剑。常给家乡的兄弟姐妹写信。

收录于：[color=#7A6352]宾博殿堂[/color]
description_tchinese:
壯得像座山，可靠又沉穩，但偏偏握不好劍。常寫信給遠方的兄弟姊妹。

收錄於：[color=#7A6352]賓博殿堂[/color]

name: Eva The Assassin
description:
She is not blind by the way, she just thinks the blindfold is cool.

Included in: [color=#7A6352]Hall Of Bimbo[/color]
description_schinese:
顺便说一句，她不是瞎的，只是觉得眼罩很酷。

收录于：[color=#7A6352]宾博殿堂[/color]
description_tchinese:
她不是瞎子，只是覺得蒙眼布很帥。

收錄於：[color=#7A6352]賓博殿堂[/color]

name: Ookar The Dwarf
description:
Don't let his height fool you, he is slightly above average amongst his peers.

Included in: [color=#7A6352]Hall Of Bimbo[/color]
description_schinese:
别被他的身高骗了，他在同族里算是略高一点的。

收录于：[color=#7A6352]宾博殿堂[/color]
description_tchinese:
別被他的身高唬住，在同族裡他其實略高於平均值。

收錄於：[color=#7A6352]賓博殿堂[/color]

name: Lora The Samurai
description:
A transfer student from a faraway Eastern Kingdom. He is friendly, just shy.

Included in: [color=#7A6352]Hall Of Bimbo[/color]
description_schinese:
来自遥远东方王国的转学生。很友好，就是害羞。

收录于：[color=#7A6352]宾博殿堂[/color]
description_tchinese:
來自遙遠東方王國的轉學生，個性和善，只是有點害羞。

收錄於：[color=#7A6352]賓博殿堂[/color]

name: Goddalf
description:
The previous headmaster, most of the ale went to him. No one knows how powerful he really is.

Included in: [color=#7A6352]Hall Of Bimbo[/color]
description_schinese:
前任校长，大部分麦芽酒都进了他的肚子。没人知道他真正有多强大。

收录于：[color=#7A6352]宾博殿堂[/color]
description_tchinese:
前任校長，酒大多進了他肚子。真正的實力有多強，沒人敢說。

收錄於：[color=#7A6352]賓博殿堂[/color]

name: Pixiu
description:
A symbol of wealth, protection and good fortune. Be sure to put this in your home!

Included in: [color=#8C8650]BaoBao Legends[/color]
description_schinese:
象征财富、守护与好运。记得把它放在家里！

收录于：[color=#8C8650]宝宝传奇[/color]
description_tchinese:
象徵財富、守護與好運，記得放一尊在家裡討吉利！

收錄於：[color=#8C8650]寶寶傳奇[/color]

name: Xiezhi
description:
Very sharp horns and a very sharp mind. If they can talk, they will be an amazing lawyer.

Included in: [color=#8C8650]BaoBao Legends[/color]
description_schinese:
犄角锋利，头脑也一样锋利。要是能说话，那绝对是个超级律师。

收录于：[color=#8C8650]宝宝传奇[/color]
description_tchinese:
犄角銳利，頭腦更銳利。若牠能說話，大概能把人辯到服氣。

收錄於：[color=#8C8650]寶寶傳奇[/color]

name: Bai Ze
description:
A symbolism of great wisdom. A wise creature this is.

Included in: [color=#8C8650]BaoBao Legends[/color]
description_schinese:
象征大智慧的生物。一只真正聪慧的家伙。

收录于：[color=#8C8650]宝宝传奇[/color]
description_tchinese:
象徵大智慧的生物，的確是非常聰明。

收錄於：[color=#8C8650]寶寶傳奇[/color]

name: Fenghuang
description:
This magnificent creature is supposed to have more colors. Too bad it looks like a rooster due to budget cuts.

Included in: [color=#8C8650]BaoBao Legends[/color]
description_schinese:
这只壮丽的生物原本应该更五彩斑斓。可惜因为预算削减，现在看起来更像只公鸡。

收录于：[color=#8C8650]宝宝传奇[/color]
description_tchinese:
原本應該五彩繽紛，可惜因為預算縮水，現在比較像隻公雞。

收錄於：[color=#8C8650]寶寶傳奇[/color]

name: Ao
description:
A large turtle. His fate is very moving, although he won't be doing much moving anytime soon.

Included in: [color=#8C8650]BaoBao Legends[/color]
description_schinese:
一只巨大的龟。它的命运十分感人，但它短期内不会有什么“行动”了。

收录于：[color=#8C8650]宝宝传奇[/color]
description_tchinese:
巨大的龜，命運可歌可泣，但短期內應該不會怎麼動。

收錄於：[color=#8C8650]寶寶傳奇[/color]

name: Qilin
description:
Harmless, gentle, immortal. They might be vegetarian as well.

Included in: [color=#8C8650]BaoBao Legends[/color]
description_schinese:
无害、温和、不朽。可能还是素食主义者。

收录于：[color=#8C8650]宝宝传奇[/color]
description_tchinese:
無害、溫柔又不死身，搞不好還吃素。

收錄於：[color=#8C8650]寶寶傳奇[/color]

name: Monkey King
description:
I've heard he's going East this time around.

Included in: [color=#8C8650]BaoBao Legends[/color]
description_schinese:
听说这次他往东边走了。

收录于：[color=#8C8650]宝宝传奇[/color]
description_tchinese:
聽說這次他要往東邊去了。

收錄於：[color=#8C8650]寶寶傳奇[/color]

name: Loong
description:
Soaring through the skies, the loong shows dominance with its immense strength

Included in: [color=#8C8650]BaoBao Legends[/color]
description_schinese:
翱翔天际，以强大力量展示威严。

收录于：[color=#8C8650]宝宝传奇[/color]
description_tchinese:
在天空中翱翔，以壓倒性力量展現威勢。

收錄於：[color=#8C8650]寶寶傳奇[/color]

name: Koala
description:
Tree dwellers that have the perfect work-life balance of 20 hour sleeps, only one can dream.

Included in: [color=#527A57]Animal Kingdom[/color]
description_schinese:
树栖动物，拥有完美的工作与生活平衡：每天睡 20 小时，真是羡慕啊。

收录于：[color=#527A57]动物王国[/color]
description_tchinese:
住在樹上的小懶蟲，20 小時睡眠的完美生活，真令人羨慕。

收錄於：[color=#527A57]動物王國[/color]

name: Panda
description:
The only animal used as a diplomatic ammo. Very lazy and very cute.

Included in: [color=#527A57]Animal Kingdom[/color]
description_schinese:
唯一一个被用作外交手段的动物。非常懒，也非常可爱。

收录于：[color=#527A57]动物王国[/color]
description_tchinese:
唯一被拿來當外交用途的動物，又懶又可愛。

收錄於：[color=#527A57]動物王國[/color]

name: Rabbit
description:
This is a common drop animal. Because just like their IRL counterparts, they'll multiply like crazy.

Included in: [color=#527A57]Animal Kingdom[/color]
description_schinese:
这是常见掉落的动物。因为和现实一样，繁殖速度快得离谱。

收录于：[color=#527A57]动物王国[/color]
description_tchinese:
普通掉落的動物，因為跟現實一樣，繁殖速度快得驚人。

收錄於：[color=#527A57]動物王國[/color]

name: Fox
description:
Have we figured out what does the fox say yet?

Included in: [color=#527A57]Animal Kingdom[/color]
description_schinese:
我们搞清楚狐狸到底会说什么了吗？

收录于：[color=#527A57]动物王国[/color]
description_tchinese:
我們到底找出狐狸會說什麼了嗎？

收錄於：[color=#527A57]動物王國[/color]

name: Hedgehog
description:
Did you know that they are not prickly as you think they are. Still handle with care.

Included in: [color=#527A57]Animal Kingdom[/color]
description_schinese:
你知道它们其实没有你想象中那么扎吗？不过还是小心点好。

收录于：[color=#527A57]动物王国[/color]
description_tchinese:
其實沒有你想像中那麼刺，但還是小心一點比較好。

收錄於：[color=#527A57]動物王國[/color]

name: Beaver
description:
Nature's first hydrolauic engineers before it was cool and energy efficient.

Included in: [color=#527A57]Animal Kingdom[/color]
description_schinese:
自然界最早的水利工程师，比现代工程还酷、还节能。

收录于：[color=#527A57]动物王国[/color]
description_tchinese:
牠們是大自然最早的水利工程師，比現代工程還潮還省能。

收錄於：[color=#527A57]動物王國[/color]

name: Capybara
description:
Those eyes may look like they can only look on their sides, but no they can stare into your soul.

Included in: [color=#527A57]Animal Kingdom[/color]
description_schinese:
他们的眼睛看起来像是只能看两边，但其实能直视你的灵魂。

收录于：[color=#527A57]动物王国[/color]
description_tchinese:
看似只能往兩側看，但其實可以直盯你的靈魂。

收錄於：[color=#527A57]動物王國[/color]

name: Red Panda
description:
Despite their name, these cute critters are in no way related to normal vanilla pandas.

Included in: [color=#527A57]Animal Kingdom[/color]
description_schinese:
尽管名字如此，这些小可爱跟普通熊猫一点关系都没有。

收录于：[color=#527A57]动物王国[/color]
description_tchinese:
名字雖然有熊貓，但跟真正的熊貓一點關係都沒有。

收錄於：[color=#527A57]動物王國[/color]

name: Octopus
description:
These inky menances have three hearts. Well I have 4 diamonds so I win.

Included in: [color=#52717A]Aquatic Life[/color]
description_schinese:
这些墨汁恶魔有三颗心。不过我有四颗钻石，所以我赢了。

收录于：[color=#52717A]水域生灵[/color]
description_tchinese:
這些墨色小惡棍有三顆心。不過我有四顆鑽石，所以我贏了。

收錄於：[color=#52717A]水域生靈[/color]

name: Crabby
description:
They can make amazing drummers.

Included in: [color=#52717A]Aquatic Life[/color]
description_schinese:
它们是很棒的鼓手。

收录于：[color=#52717A]水域生灵[/color]
description_tchinese:
牠們可以當超強鼓手。

收錄於：[color=#52717A]水域生靈[/color]

name: Sharky
description:
Please do not ask why he has legs. Doo, doo, doo, doo, doo, doo.

Included in: [color=#52717A]Aquatic Life[/color]
description_schinese:
请别问他为什么有腿。嘟、嘟、嘟、嘟、嘟、嘟。

收录于：[color=#52717A]水域生灵[/color]
description_tchinese:
別問他為什麼有腿。嘟、嘟、嘟、嘟、嘟、嘟。

收錄於：[color=#52717A]水域生靈[/color]

name: Seal
description:
Here's a question, do seals sleep in land or in water?

Included in: [color=#52717A]Aquatic Life[/color]
description_schinese:
问题来了：海豹是在陆地上睡觉还是在水里睡觉？

收录于：[color=#52717A]水域生灵[/color]
description_tchinese:
問題來了：海豹到底在陸地睡還是在水裡睡？

收錄於：[color=#52717A]水域生靈[/color]

name: Axoloti
description:
They regenerate everything, I mean everything. :)

Included in: [color=#52717A]Aquatic Life[/color]
description_schinese:
他们能再生任何东西，我是说任何东西。:)

收录于：[color=#52717A]水域生灵[/color]
description_tchinese:
牠們能再生所有東西，真的所有東西。:)

收錄於：[color=#52717A]水域生靈[/color]

name: Whale
description:
One of the smarter critters of the deep blue. Their songs are still up to interpretation.

Included in: [color=#52717A]Aquatic Life[/color]
description_schinese:
深海中最聪明的生物之一。它们的歌声至今仍无法完全解读。

收录于：[color=#52717A]水域生灵[/color]
description_tchinese:
深海中最聰明的生物之一，牠們的歌聲至今仍眾說紛紜。

收錄於：[color=#52717A]水域生靈[/color]

name: Penguin
description:
A cute little critter in the arctic, now in a sharp two-tone look.

Included in: [color=#52717A]Aquatic Life[/color]
description_schinese:
来自北极的小可爱，如今拥有时尚的双色外套。

收录于：[color=#52717A]水域生灵[/color]
description_tchinese:
來自極地的小可愛，現在穿著俐落的黑白雙色大衣。

收錄於：[color=#52717A]水域生靈[/color]

name: Seahorse
description:
Has nothing to do with our land-based horses. Male seahorses have it rough however.

Included in: [color=#52717A]Aquatic Life[/color]
description_schinese:
和陆地上的马一点关系都没有。不过雄海马确实很惨。

收录于：[color=#52717A]水域生灵[/color]
description_tchinese:
跟陸地馬完全無關，但雄海馬真的很辛苦。

收錄於：[color=#52717A]水域生靈[/color]

name: Crimson Father
description:
The head honcho, the man himself. Don't tell his wife but he always gets his advice from the Cultist, he is an amazing wingman.

Included in: [color=#902D2D]Crimson Feathers[/color]
description_schinese:
大头领，本人亲至。别告诉他老婆，他的建议其实都是从信徒那儿来的，对方是个绝佳僚机。

收录于：[color=#902D2D]深红之羽[/color]
description_tchinese:
大頭目本人。別跟他老婆講，他的建議其實都是信徒幫忙想的。

收錄於：[color=#902D2D]深紅之羽[/color]

name: Crimson Cultist
description:
Your father's chief advisor and spiritual consultant. Don't let those horns fool you, they are not made of gold.

Included in: [color=#902D2D]Crimson Feathers[/color]
description_schinese:
你父亲的首席顾问和精神导师。别被那对角骗了，它们可不是金的。

收录于：[color=#902D2D]深红之羽[/color]
description_tchinese:
你父親的首席顧問與精神指導，別被那對角騙了，絕對不是金的。

收錄於：[color=#902D2D]深紅之羽[/color]

name: Crimson Knight
description:
Tha mansion's security unit, numbering in the hundreds. They always stood still, guarding, wearing impractical and needlessly expensive gear.

Included in: [color=#902D2D]Crimson Feathers[/color]
description_schinese:
庄园的安保单位，多达数百。他们永远静立不动，守卫着，穿着昂贵又不实用的盔甲。

收录于：[color=#902D2D]深红之羽[/color]
description_tchinese:
莊園的安保部隊，數量成百上千，永遠站著不動守衛，盔甲貴得離譜。

收錄於：[color=#902D2D]深紅之羽[/color]

name: Crimson Devil
description:
Father's experimental specimen at the mansion's lower levels. Can give you strength training advice.

Included in: [color=#902D2D]Crimson Feathers[/color]
description_schinese:
父亲在庄园地下室的实验品。可以给你力量训练建议。

收录于：[color=#902D2D]深红之羽[/color]
description_tchinese:
父親在地下室打造的實驗體，可以順便教你重量訓練。

收錄於：[color=#902D2D]深紅之羽[/color]

name: Crimson Mother
description:
Title holder for the longest happy marriage in recent memory. Dislikes her husband's advisors.

Included in: [color=#902D2D]Crimson Feathers[/color]
description_schinese:
保持最幸福婚姻时间最长的持有者。讨厌她丈夫的顾问们。

收录于：[color=#902D2D]深红之羽[/color]
description_tchinese:
最長久幸福婚姻的保持人，但很不喜歡老公的那些顧問。

收錄於：[color=#902D2D]深紅之羽[/color]

name: Crimson Daughter
description:
Proud heir of the family. Smart, kind and resourceful. Likes blades and piano, dislikes her brother and the sorceress.

Included in: [color=#902D2D]Crimson Feathers[/color]
description_schinese:
家族的骄傲继承人。聪明、善良、机智。喜欢刀和钢琴，不喜欢她哥哥和女术士。

收录于：[color=#902D2D]深红之羽[/color]
description_tchinese:
家族的驕傲繼承人，聰明、善良又機靈。喜歡刀與鋼琴，不喜歡哥哥與女術士。

收錄於：[color=#902D2D]深紅之羽[/color]

name: Crimson Son
description:
Looks young, he might act like a kid but he sure ain't one.

Included in: [color=#902D2D]Crimson Feathers[/color]
description_schinese:
看起来年轻，行为也像孩子，但他可绝对不是。

收录于：[color=#902D2D]深红之羽[/color]
description_tchinese:
看起來很年輕，行為像小孩，但他絕對不是。

收錄於：[color=#902D2D]深紅之羽[/color]

name: Crimson Sorceress
description:
Adept at all forms of necromancy, tutors the kids regularly. Still single.

Included in: [color=#792F2F]Crimson Feathers[/color]
description_schinese:
精通各种死灵术，定期辅导孩子。依然单身。

收录于：[color=#792F2F]深红之羽[/color]
description_tchinese:
精通各種死靈術，還會定期家教小朋友，目前仍單身。

收錄於：[color=#792F2F]深紅之羽[/color]

name: The Silent God
description:
The outsider from the other realm, powerful beyond belief. Consider your fate sealed if you see it.

Included in: [color=#605A4E]The Silent Arcana[/color]
description_schinese:
来自其他领域的异界者，强大到无法想象。若你看见祂，命运已定。

收录于：[color=#605A4E]寂静奥秘[/color]
description_tchinese:
來自異界的存在，強大得不可思議。看到他時，你的命運就定了。

收錄於：[color=#605A4E]寂靜奧秘[/color]

name: Skelly Belly
description:
The remnants of those who have listened to the whispers, no one knows why they turned into babies. That matter is still up for debate, but they had more pressing matters at hand.

Included in: [color=#605A4E]The Silent Arcana[/color]
description_schinese:
那些听从低语之人的残余。没人知道他们为何变成婴儿，这仍是个争论点。但他们还有更紧迫的麻烦。

收录于：[color=#605A4E]寂静奥秘[/color]
description_tchinese:
那些聽信低語者的殘餘，變成嬰兒的原因仍眾說紛紜，但他們有更急的問題。

收錄於：[color=#605A4E]寂靜奧秘[/color]

name: Plaguey Doctor
description:
A creature from another realm, the silent gods' medical arm. Their syringe can fetch a high price.

Included in: [color=#605A4E]The Silent Arcana[/color]
description_schinese:
来自他界生物，是寂静之神的医疗部门。它的注射器能卖个好价钱。

收录于：[color=#605A4E]寂静奥秘[/color]
description_tchinese:
異界來的生物，寂靜之神的醫療部門，牠的針筒能賣高價。

收錄於：[color=#605A4E]寂靜奧秘[/color]

name: Jesty
description:
A creature from another realm, he will tell a bad joke before killing you. If you can quip something better, he will actually leave you alone.

Included in: [color=#605A4E]The Silent Arcana[/color]
description_schinese:
来自他界的存在，会在杀你之前讲个烂笑话。如果你能接的更妙，它真的会放你走。

收录于：[color=#605A4E]寂静奥秘[/color]
description_tchinese:
異界來的傢伙，殺你前會先講個爛笑話。如果你回得更好，他真的會放你走。

收錄於：[color=#605A4E]寂靜奧秘[/color]

name: Ember Spirit
description:
The remnants of those who have listened to the whispers. Red in nature, relatively harmless.

Included in: [color=#605A4E]The Silent Arcana[/color]
description_schinese:
那些听从低语者的残留物。天性赤红，相对无害。

收录于：[color=#605A4E]寂静奥秘[/color]
description_tchinese:
低語者的殘留物，本質偏紅，算是無害。

收錄於：[color=#605A4E]寂靜奧秘[/color]

name: Hanniboo
description:
An escapee of the medical ward, the serial killer has a new, more challenging target.

Included in: [color=#605A4E]The Silent Arcana[/color]
description_schinese:
医疗病房的逃犯，这位连环杀手又盯上了一个更具挑战性的目标。

收录于：[color=#605A4E]寂静奥秘[/color]
description_tchinese:
醫療區的逃犯，這位連環殺手現在找到更有挑戰性的獵物。

收錄於：[color=#605A4E]寂靜奧秘[/color]

name: Flagellant
description:
Someone thought you can beat the arcanas into submission, we shall see.

Included in: [color=#605A4E]The Silent Arcana[/color]
description_schinese:
有人以为可以把奥秘家族打服，我们拭目以待。

收录于：[color=#605A4E]寂静奥秘[/color]
description_tchinese:
有人覺得能把奧秘系統打到服氣，拭目以待吧。

收錄於：[color=#605A4E]寂靜奧秘[/color]

name: Arcana Hunter
description:
The answer to the Arcanas, equipped with an unmistakable mask. Despite their looks, they look out for humanity.

Included in: [color=#605A4E]The Silent Arcana[/color]
description_schinese:
奥秘们的克星，戴着一眼就能认出的面具。尽管外表吓人，他们其实守护着人类。

收录于：[color=#605A4E]寂静奥秘[/color]
description_tchinese:
奧秘的克星，戴著超顯眼的面具。雖然看起來可怕，其實是在保護人類。

收錄於：[color=#605A4E]寂靜奧秘[/color]

name: Vox-Corp Patient Zero
description:
Due to financial difficulties, he works part-time as a bouncer. You do not want to mess with him.

Included in: [color=#65527A]Ravepunk City[/color]
description_schinese:
由于经济困难，他兼职做门卫。你绝对不想惹他。

收录于：[color=#65527A]炫核之城[/color]
description_tchinese:
因為財務困難而兼差當保鑣，你絕對不想惹他。

收錄於：[color=#65527A]炫核之城[/color]

name: Ghost.exe
description:
Swordsman at day, hardcore drinker at night. The club does not allow sharp objects inside its premises though.

Included in: [color=#65527A]Ravepunk City[/color]
description_schinese:
白天是剑士，晚上是酒鬼。可俱乐部不允许携带锐器入内。

收录于：[color=#65527A]炫核之城[/color]
description_tchinese:
白天是劍士，晚上是酒國英雄，但夜店禁止鋒利物品。

收錄於：[color=#65527A]炫核之城[/color]

name: Vox-Corp Militant
description:
Vox-corp's regular goons. I still remember when goon was a noun.

Included in: [color=#65527A]Ravepunk City[/color]
description_schinese:
Vox 公司常见的打手。我记得以前“goon”可是个名词。

收录于：[color=#65527A]炫核之城[/color]
description_tchinese:
Vox 公司的常駐打手。我記得 goon 以前可是名詞。

收錄於：[color=#65527A]炫核之城[/color]

name: Hugo
description:
They get surprsingly open about their jobs three drinks in, be prepared to be an on-the-spot therapist if that's the case.

Included in: [color=#65527A]Ravepunk City[/color]
description_schinese:
喝三杯后，他们居然会对自己的工作滔滔不绝。如果发生这种事，你最好准备当临时心理咨询师。

收录于：[color=#65527A]炫核之城[/color]
description_tchinese:
喝三杯後會突然敞開心胸聊工作，你最好準備好當臨時心理諮商師。

收錄於：[color=#65527A]炫核之城[/color]

name: Cael
description:
Unemployed, couch surfer, resident troublemaker. A good fellow to be around.

Included in: [color=#65527A]Ravepunk City[/color]
description_schinese:
失业、蹭沙发的常驻麻烦制造者。是个不错的朋友。

收录于：[color=#65527A]炫核之城[/color]
description_tchinese:
失業、沙發客、在地麻煩製造者，但其實人很不錯。

收錄於：[color=#65527A]炫核之城[/color]

name: Nira
description:
The newcomer, visibly lacking in augments. The club is her sole escape for the horrid work-life balance.

Included in: [color=#65527A]Ravepunk City[/color]
description_schinese:
新人，明显缺乏改造。俱乐部是她逃离糟糕工作生活唯一的出口。

收录于：[color=#65527A]炫核之城[/color]
description_tchinese:
新來的，改造程度明顯不足，夜店是她逃離爛生活的唯一出口。

收錄於：[color=#65527A]炫核之城[/color]

name: Vicky Lovely
description:
A regular. Whatever you do, do not join her after closing hours.

Included in: [color=#65527A]Ravepunk City[/color]
description_schinese:
常客。不管你做什么，都千万别在打烊后跟她一起走。

收录于：[color=#65527A]炫核之城[/color]
description_tchinese:
老主顧。無論如何，打烊後千萬別跟她一起走。

收錄於：[color=#65527A]炫核之城[/color]

name: Vera The Sentinel
description:
The tubes at his sides can turn into straws for his cocktails.

Included in: [color=#65527A]Ravepunk City[/color]
description_schinese:
他两侧的管子可以变成鸡尾酒用的吸管。

收录于：[color=#65527A]炫核之城[/color]
description_tchinese:
他身側的管子可以變成吸雞尾酒的吸管。

收錄於：[color=#65527A]炫核之城[/color]

name: Colornaut
description:
Boarding the ship filled with paint is not easy, let's just say some inventory was lost.

Included in: [color=#8B827C]Dreamy Voyage[/color]
description_schinese:
登上装满颜料的船可不容易，可以说有些库存“丢失”了。

收录于：[color=#8B827C]梦幻旅程[/color]
description_tchinese:
登上載滿顏料的船不容易，可以說……有些物資『遺失』了。

收錄於：[color=#8B827C]夢幻旅程[/color]

name: Friendly Anomaly
description:
Now we are just lying, how does that look friendly?

Included in: [color=#8B827C]Dreamy Voyage[/color]
description_schinese:
我们现在根本是在撒谎，那哪里看起来友好？

收录于：[color=#8B827C]梦幻旅程[/color]
description_tchinese:
我們是在騙誰？這哪裡看起來友善？

收錄於：[color=#8B827C]夢幻旅程[/color]

name: FLOO-E
description:
Colornaut's helper during the voyage. Although it does not have oppasable thumbs, it is mostly there for moral support.

Included in: [color=#8B827C]Dreamy Voyage[/color]
description_schinese:
在航程中帮助 Colornaut 的助手。虽然它没有对生拇指，但主要负责精神支持。

收录于：[color=#8B827C]梦幻旅程[/color]
description_tchinese:
航行途中協助 Colornaut 的助手，雖然沒有拇指，但主要負責精神支援。

收錄於：[color=#8B827C]夢幻旅程[/color]

name: Advanced Alien
description:
The ship's robot navigational assistant. You do not want to get on his bad side, his cousin threw a tantrum and it did not end well.

Included in: [color=#8B827C]Dreamy Voyage[/color]
description_schinese:
船上的机器人导航助手。你可不想惹他生气，他的表亲之前发过一次脾气，结果不太妙。

收录于：[color=#8B827C]梦幻旅程[/color]
description_tchinese:
船上的機器導航助手，最好別惹他，他表親上次鬧脾氣可不得了。

收錄於：[color=#8B827C]夢幻旅程[/color]

name: Bing Baug
description:
What humans think aliens should look like. They saw ET and took some notes.

Included in: [color=#8B827C]Dreamy Voyage[/color]
description_schinese:
人类认为外星人该有的样子。他们显然看过《ET》，并认真做了笔记。

收录于：[color=#8B827C]梦幻旅程[/color]
description_tchinese:
人類以為外星人應該長這樣，明顯看過 ET 並做了筆記。

收錄於：[color=#8B827C]夢幻旅程[/color]

name: Asteroid
description:
A sentient mass of rock. Rich in vitamins and minerals.

Included in: [color=#8B827C]Dreamy Voyage[/color]
description_schinese:
一块有意识的岩石。富含维生素和矿物质。

收录于：[color=#8B827C]梦幻旅程[/color]
description_tchinese:
有意識的岩石，富含維生素與礦物質。

收錄於：[color=#8B827C]夢幻旅程[/color]

name: Miss Invulnerable
description:
Carbon(?) based creature. Also struggled with the inventory.

Included in: [color=#8B827C]Dreamy Voyage[/color]
description_schinese:
类似碳（？）构成的生物，也曾在运输中遇到瓶颈。

收录于：[color=#8B827C]梦幻旅程[/color]
description_tchinese:
疑似以碳為基底的生物，也在搬運時受了不少苦。

收錄於：[color=#8B827C]夢幻旅程[/color]

name: Tardigrade
description:
What if cockroaches were more durable?

Included in: [color=#8B827C]Dreamy Voyage[/color]
description_schinese:
如果蟑螂更耐打会怎样？

收录于：[color=#8B827C]梦幻旅程[/color]
description_tchinese:
如果蟑螂更耐打會變怎樣？

收錄於：[color=#8B827C]夢幻旅程[/color]

name: Julius Caesar
description:
The leader of the Roman Empire. The salad was not named after him.

Included in: [color=#8B827C]Streets Of Rome[/color]
description_schinese:
罗马帝国的领袖。沙拉可不是以他命名的。

收录于：[color=#8B827C]罗马街道[/color]
description_tchinese:
羅馬帝國的領袖，沙拉可不是以他命名的。

收錄於：[color=#8B827C]羅馬街道[/color]

name: Themis
description:
The arbiter of justice. Her scales need recalibration once every two months.

Included in: [color=#8B827C]Streets Of Rome[/color]
description_schinese:
正义的裁决者。她的天平需要每两个月校准一次。

收录于：[color=#8B827C]罗马街道[/color]
description_tchinese:
正義的審判者，她的天平每兩個月就要重新校正。

收錄於：[color=#8B827C]羅馬街道[/color]

name: Aphrodite
description:
The god of beauty. Her makeup accounts for 2% of Rome's expenses.

Included in: [color=#8B827C]Streets Of Rome[/color]
description_schinese:
美之女神。她的化妆品占了罗马 2% 的开销。

收录于：[color=#8B827C]罗马街道[/color]
description_tchinese:
美之女神，她的妝占了羅馬 2% 的支出。

收錄於：[color=#8B827C]羅馬街道[/color]

name: Roman Commander
description:
Lead officer of the Roman Army. The feathers are not intimidating at all, but don't tell him.

Included in: [color=#8B827C]Streets Of Rome[/color]
description_schinese:
罗马军团的主要指挥官。那几根羽毛一点也不可怕，但别告诉他。

收录于：[color=#8B827C]罗马街道[/color]
description_tchinese:
羅馬軍隊的主官，頭上的羽毛一點都不可怕，但別讓他知道。

收錄於：[color=#8B827C]羅馬街道[/color]

name: Medusa
description:
One of the Gorgons. Her hair routine remains a closely guarded secret.

Included in: [color=#8B827C]Streets Of Rome[/color]
description_schinese:
三位戈耳工之一。她的头发保养方法至今是个机密。

收录于：[color=#8B827C]罗马街道[/color]
description_tchinese:
三姊妹之一的戈耳工，她的髮型秘訣到現在仍保密。

收錄於：[color=#8B827C]羅馬街道[/color]

name: Poseidon
description:
The god of the seas. He is not compensating for something.

Included in: [color=#8B827C]Streets Of Rome[/color]
description_schinese:
海神。他可没有在补偿什么。

收录于：[color=#8B827C]罗马街道[/color]
description_tchinese:
海神，他可沒有在補償什麼。

收錄於：[color=#8B827C]羅馬街道[/color]

name: Zeus
description:
The god of thunder, the lightning bolts he throws at you are made of plastic however.

Included in: [color=#8B827C]Streets Of Rome[/color]
description_schinese:
雷霆之神，不过他扔出的闪电是塑料做的。

收录于：[color=#8B827C]罗马街道[/color]
description_tchinese:
雷神，不過他丟的閃電是塑膠做的。

收錄於：[color=#8B827C]羅馬街道[/color]

name: Athena
description:
The goddess of warfare. She and Kratos had a little falling out.

Included in: [color=#8B827C]Streets Of Rome[/color]
description_schinese:
战争女神。她和奎托斯之前有点小矛盾。

收录于：[color=#8B827C]罗马街道[/color]
description_tchinese:
戰爭女神，她跟奎托斯之前鬧過點小矛盾。

收錄於：[color=#8B827C]羅馬街道[/color]

name: Voucher
description: Used to purchase blind boxes in the blind box shop in the game called Blind Box!
description_schinese: 用于在《Blind Box》游戏的盲盒商店中购买盲盒的代币。
description_tchinese: 用於在《Blind Box》遊戲的盲盒商店中購買盲盒的代幣。

name: Kitty
description:
A thank you gift to launch players! Meow <3.

[color=#ff9600]Unique[/color]
description_schinese:
送给上线玩家的感谢礼物！喵 <3

[color=#ff9600]独特[/color]
description_tchinese:
送給上線玩家的感謝小禮物！喵 <3

[color=#ff9600]獨特[/color]
